16 TO MODIFY THE DEFINITION OF "HEALTHCARE
17 PROVIDER" REGARDING STUDENT ATHLETE
18 CONCUSSION EDUCATION TO INCLUDE
19 CHIROPRACTORS OR CHIROPRACTIC
20 PHYSICIANS.
21
22 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
23
24 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 6-18-710(a)(1), as amended by ยง 1 of Acts
25 2025, No. 266, concerning the definition of "healthcare provider" relating to
26 student athlete concussion education, is amended to read as follows:
27 (1) "Healthcare provider" means an allopathic or osteopathic
28 physician, neuropsychologist, chiropractor or chiropractic physician,
29 advanced practice registered nurse, certified athletic trainer, physician
30 assistant, or physical therapist; and
